textBeforeTable: These tags are found in .MOS images from Leaf digital camera backs as written by Creo Leaf Capture. They exist within the Leaf-specific directory structure of EXIF tag 0x8606. The tables below list observed Leaf tags, however ExifTool will extract any tags found in the Leaf directories even if they don't appear in these tables. Leaf Tags
